$Id$
------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains the shell wrapper for the xindy-system.

The Makefile can be adjusted to set the default path for xindy. Typing
`make' generates the shell-script `xindy' with the defined
default-path which defaults to /usr/local/lib/xindy.

Enjoy, Roger.

